//////////////////////////////////////////////////////////////////////////////////////////////////////////////////////////////////////////////////////
01. Installation

    Architecture
        Address Space >
            Node 1
                Var 1 (Temperature)
                Var 2 (Pressure)
                Var 3 (Time)
            Node 2
            Node 3

    Installation 
        FreeOPCUA
            https://github.com/FreeOpcUa/python-opcua
        Python 3.5 required
        Go to Python installation directory
        Enter 'scripts' folder
        C:\>Python3.5\Scripts>pip3 install freeopcua
        C:\>Python3.5\Scripts>pip3 install cryptography
        

